+ Transition:
+ la chuyen tiep giua 2 trang thai
  + transition: width
  + transition: [ten thuoc tinh] [thoi gian] [timing function]
  + transition-property:
    + tat ca cac thuoc tinh bang so
      + width, height, padding, margin, border-width
      + color, font-size, left, top...
      + color: so
  + transition-duration:
  + transition-timing-function:

+ Transition: anh huong den kich thuoc

+ Tat ca cac thuoc tinh css:
