+ media query: responsive

@media [loai man hinh]
@media screen and (dieu kien)

@media print and (dieu kien)

+ Break point:
  + La nhung diem: thay doi cach hien thi
  + > 1200px => man hinh extra large
  + > 960px => man hinh lon
  + > 768px => man hinh trung binh
  + < 768px => man hinh nho

mobile first
  + code cho man hinh mobile truoc
  + tu nho => to
  + bootstrap => mobile first

desktop first
  + code cho man hinh to
  => nho dan

